            <h2>IIIBF Alumni</h2>
            <p style="text-align:justify">The Alumni is the esteemed body that brings together all the former students of the International Institute of Islamic banking and finance, Bayero University, Kano. It is an association which ensures that its members live with the trainings and ethics always. 
                The National body is the umbrella and apex body with state offices and branches in organisations. The National body coordinates all the national and international activities of the association, and also takes care of the registration of new members. 
                The members are people from different walks of life who went through a rigorous training in order to achieve excellence, to provide and practice excellence anywhere in the world.</p>
            
        </div>
               
