            <h2>History</h2>
            <p style="text-align:justify">The Institute’s commitment began in 2011 with a four component mission: teaching, research, scholarship, and service provision. The vision of the IIIBF is to be a world class institute offering professional and academic training and certification in Islamic banking and finance throughout Africa and beyond. Its mission is to extend the frontiers of knowledge of Islamic banking and finance nationally and internationally with enthusiasm, dedication and professionalism with a view to producing high quality human resources, rich in entrepreneurial skills for the development of mankind. 
                The core values of the institute is the Islamisation of knowledge, integration and internationalisation, professionalism and good governance, humility and sacrifice, discipline and commitment, excellence and best practices.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
