            <h2>Vision</h2>
            <p style="text-align:justify">The clear vision of the association is to provide a platform for the alumnus to rekindle their commitment and foster individual and collective obligation for harnessing the abundant reservoir of goodwill by deploying critical resources for the upliftment of our alma mater as a foremost fountain of integrity and knowledge of Islamic banking and finance in Africa.</p>
